Shell Study Notes by Tiancheng Gong (TLCL Chapter 2)

X Window System:
    copy text: highlight the text using left mouse button (double-click or drag)
    paste text: press the middle mouse button

date -- Display the current time and date

cal -- Display a calendar of the current month

df -- Display the current amount of free space on the disk drivers

free -- Display the amount of the free memory

exit -- Exit the terminal
